name: Photo Finish PFP Collection
description: A 15,000-piece combined collection of Stylish Studs and Marvelous Mares. They came together to produce the very first racehorses in Photo Finish™ LIVE - laying down the bloodlines that run through every horse in the game. PFP owners are VIP’s in the ecosystem, earning $CROWN based on overall rarity, and have access to the exclusive Photo Finish Jockey Club.
